name: The Girl in Leda's Dress
description: A piece about power and revenge, justice and elegance. A girl in an enchanted dress, drenched in mystery and radiant magic. A reaction to "Leda and the Swan", except this time, there is no more swan. Only its blood, staining the flow of peaceful, healing waters. No gods can dip, or they shall be devoured. It was Zeus. He did it to himself.
